<h3><a href="/about/careers/life.html">Life at CableLabs</a></h3>
<p>CableLabs is able to accomplish its work by bringing talented people together in a supportive, collaborative environment. We reward hard work. We applaud innovation. We welcome daily challenge.</p>
<h3><a href="/about/careers/community.html">CableLabs Community</a></h3>
<p>We at CableLabs support our external and internal communities.</p>

<h3>&nbsp;</h3></td>
